data.title: 20 Qs at Questacon — Prof Alan R Duffy
data.meta_description: Questacon is the national science and technology centre and an absolute treat to get to spend a day visiting  but  the questions I was asked when there were so tough! What would you have answered?
data.text: Questacon is the national science and technology centre and an absolute treat to get to spend a day visiting but the questions I was asked when there were so tough! Although perhaps I shouldn’t be surprised as it’s been educating and engaging Australia and our international partners in STEM for over thirty years. What would you have answered?
